channel.title: MooScape 5.0 - RuneScape Client
channel.description:
Hi, i have just finished creating MooScape 5.0!
It is a RuneScape client with many features which are listed on the official MooScape website located here: http://www.powelly.com/mooscape/
Please note to anyone doubting MooScape saying 'omg keylogger111' etc, that i have been creating RuneScape clients since the days of RuneScape Classic and i am the most original client programmer to date (allot of other clients like stealing my ideas :P)
Cheers, Powelly

InStiNcT:

Faketrix has been making programs since before I can remember. Back in the day, about... 5 years ago when I played habbo hotel (yeah yeah, shut up) Faketrix made some bad ass programs. Habbo hotel used to be cool when you could be invisible and make mutants and block doorways, I miss the old days

I've also used Faketrix's client, it was the first RS2 client I ever used for RS2, It was very nice and customizable color backrounds, was pretty cool, I reccommend trying this client out.
